title: Hunger-Man 0.95 - 2d Arcade Style Game
description:
Have fun in this arcade style point eater game. The goal is to eat all the points before the timer runs out. To get even more points you will need to turn the 'Worbles' into food. This game feature an online scoreboard; however the game will still run if your offline. You just won't be able to view or uses the scoreboard. 	

Updates:

Fixed scoreboard for larger names.
Added level 7.
Fixed actor path AI.
